{"tid":119574,"cid":31,"subCid":0,"title":"今日搭巴士個陣專登係d廢老面前咳 增強佢地既抵抗力","createTime":"2017-02-14T00:28:57.000Z","updateTime":"2017-02-14T01:57:13.000Z","uid":33359,"like":7,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"1c730cf453474ff500d7162185d68c09f3ec600d","tid":119574,"uid":33359,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-14T00:28:57.000Z","msg":"話說琴日開始有d感冒 有d頭痛又咳得好西利下<br />\n今朝一上廢老專車1a 就見到成班廢老係到妹下妹下霸哂成架車<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/33.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n其實真係唔明d廢老咁早起身搭車為乜<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/28.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n聽講將感冒傳比人自己就可以好得快d<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/35.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n而感冒好返之後抵抗力都會好左<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/38.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n所以我就專登係班廢老面前大大力咳<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n希望可以幫佢地增強抵抗力啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/38.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ad0582763c64c1e6d7ef8468b4481c638fc6d8db","tid":119574,"uid":33359,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-14T00:42:36.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/38.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"aa0c38399dad970f37353531f4a82f23811d7a4d","tid":119574,"uid":77191,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-14T00:49:58.000Z","msg":"Ching ho ball<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/38.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2f946cd3a8f899460179c32da66149d6c03d0c4f","tid":119574,"uid":44945,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-14T00:56:12.000Z","msg":"十卜清"},{"pid":"8d6c2c6bcacd858d7ab5c953c3af4055082645f0","tid":119574,"uid":33359,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-14T01:14:14.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/38.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"22596658d421318d9226e52abbdc91d4bbc0340b","tid":119574,"uid":15872,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02